She's only six years old and already a hit on the decks. That's Cape Town’s youngest female DJ. Sophia Petersen has been getting the party started with her jams, and even remixes her favourite cartoon songs. Tanya Nefdt has more. Courtesy #DStv403  CAPE TOWN - She's only 6 years old and already a hit on the decks. Sophia Petersen is Cape Town’s youngest female DJ. She's been getting the party started with her jams, and even remixes her favourite cartoon songs. With her tiny little fingers, Sophia -- two years ago already -- remixed the popular Baby Shark tune. It's been played at a number of house parties. * Tanya Nefdt has more. Watch the full video report above.